{"tid":2179732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[動L]成龍北京豪宅被拍賣 入住13年突遭查封","createTime":"2020-08-29T10:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T08:56:28.000Z","uid":66246,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"40cca12d25133f446f3ce8f3a127f521f060fb5d","tid":2179732,"uid":66246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T10:35:50.000Z","msg":"8月28日，有大陸網友爆料稱，成龍在北京東城區東直門內大街的豪宅正在拍賣。網上資料顯示，位於9號院2號樓的1001室和1002室的面積共1,217.5平方米，起拍價7,190萬元（人民幣，下同）。<br />\n<br />\n陸媒「網易娛樂」28日向圈內知名娛記求證，對方表示，成龍確實在這裡有房子，並透露，成龍的兒子房祖名與台灣藝人柯震東2014年吸毒被抓，就是發生在這套豪宅裡。<br />\n目前在「法拍網」已經可以查詢到該房產的拍賣信息，上面顯示，已有18人圍觀，成龍的兩套豪宅將於2020年9月28日上午10點開拍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2yEpyOe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2yEpyOe.jpg&h=e7f91ce5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a43005a59d72f9b89f355d9c44edc92474cddabf","tid":2179732,"uid":327462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:34:18.000Z","msg":"支那人是要管的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3acfef5f55f20270692588e03c73ac9367526f","tid":2179732,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:38:09.000Z","msg":"住左13年顯然左祖國既仁慈"},{"pid":"6fc37e843c314edbf0790816261e74b5916cbcb9","tid":2179732,"uid":296369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:49:14.000Z","msg":"當送比祖國啦⋯⋯"},{"pid":"b79c5091fb19a70f3497e8278507a0d99b050bff","tid":2179732,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:56:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/se5cH8r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fse5cH8r.jpg&h=63214955&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6762bfde0fa387bd9e24390aee46efa71c8a362f","tid":2179732,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T08:56:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=j8-AmBGNur4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F